=== The_Alternative ===
So if VPN bans don't work, what do we do? # diagram: parental_controls.png

We need to accept that VPN bans aren't viable and find better approaches.

The solution isn't trying to block access with technology that can be easily bypassed.

It's providing tools and approaches that work regardless of VPNs:
- On-device parental controls
- Router-level content filtering
- App-specific feature gating
- Education for parents and children
- Open communication
- Investment in offline social spaces

These approaches don't rely on identifying everyone online or blocking VPN traffic.

They work at the point of accessâ€”the device itself.

